      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "This AP2-generation chassis represents the zenith of naturally aspirated engineering. Powered by the longitudinal F22C1 inline-four, this unit features a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline and remains entirely stock. The six-speed close-ratio manual transmission exhibits crisp synchronization across all gates, delivering power to the rear wheels via the original Torsen limited-slip differential. The double-wishbone suspension geometry remains tight with zero bushing degradation, ensuring surgical turn-in and high-speed stability. The exterior retains its factory-correct finish with no discernible imperfections, while the cabin is a time capsule, featuring pristine leather bolsters and fully functional digital instrumentation. A collector-grade example for the discerning purist seeking an unmolested driving experience.",
